  "detailed_description": "An extinction event rendered a life-bearing planet to still silence. Millennia later, deep beneath the planet's surface something is stirring.... <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830210/extras/ad949bf8b7cf6a5cefa6e09fe02ba3d0.poster.avif?t=1772820576\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830210/extras/ad949bf8b7cf6a5cefa6e09fe02ba3d0.webm?t=1772820576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830210/extras/ad949bf8b7cf6a5cefa6e09fe02ba3d0.mp4?t=1772820576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830210/extras/11c6a250b23e2ae39c67309f342b9209.poster.avif?t=1772820576\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830210/extras/11c6a250b23e2ae39c67309f342b9209.webm?t=1772820576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830210/extras/11c6a250b23e2ae39c67309f342b9209.mp4?t=1772820576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830210/extras/30903d0a7683b566fa0bb272d77b7a6c.poster.avif?t=1772820576\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830210/extras/30903d0a7683b566fa0bb272d77b7a6c.webm?t=1772820576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830210/extras/30903d0a7683b566fa0bb272d77b7a6c